  <brief_title>Frailty and Postoperative Shock</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Université Catholique de Louvain</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Université Catholique de Louvain</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To find an objective, affordable and manageable way to measure frailty in elderly patients
      and to examine relationship between peri-operative metabolism of frail older people and
      outcome after hip surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
